<h1> ‚òï Dalgona Coffee Recipe ‚òï</h1>
<img src = "https://i1.faceprep.in/ProGrad/dalgona-coffee-image.png" alt = "Dalgona coffee image">

<p>This yummy South Korean coffee treat that's all over the internet only requires four ingredients to make - all of which you probably have in the cupboard ‚Äì you feel like you‚Äôve won the jackpot, right?</p>

<h2>Ingredients </h2>
<ul>
  <li> Instant Coffee or Expresso Granules</li>
  <li> Sugar </li>
  <li> Hot water </li>
  <li> Milk </li>
</ul>
<h2> Dalgona Making Process </h2>

<!---bold the required contents--->
<dl>
  <dt><strong> Step 1: Combine the instant coffee, sugar, and hot water:</strong></dt>
    <dd>Add 2 tablespoons (tbsp) of instant coffee, 2 tbsp of sugar, and 2 tbsp of hot water to a medium mixing bowl. </dd></br>
  <dt><strong> Step 2: Whisk, whisk, whisk until the coffee is light and fluffy!</strong></dt>
  <dd>Using an electric hand-held mixer, whip the coffee mixture until it is light brown, fluffy, and holds stiff peaks when the whisk is removed.
</dd></br>
  <dt><strong> Step 3: Serve with Milk:</strong></dt>
  <dd>Use a spoon to garnish a glass of hot or cold milk with the coffee cream. Serve with a straw, and stir, stir, stir to enjoy!</dd></br>
</dl>

